snippet.textDisplay: I still remember ... last year when someone very close to me fell seriously ill and had to be rushed to the hospital. Received a call from her mother late in the night while i was watching this episode of CS, asking me to come visit her in the hospital. As i was hurriedly getting ready to leave, this song was playing. Sitting outside the ICU praying for her well being,  the words  forever etched into my mind Main yahan hun muntazir, tum wahan ho bekhabar ....
